# Fitur Query Tambahan (Analitik API)

Selain operasi CRUD, API harus memiliki fitur analitik menggunakan parameter **action**.

Contoh:

```
GET /games.php?action=topSalesGames
```

Fitur yang harus tersedia:

### Statistik

```
countGames
countUsers
countPurchases
```

---

### Analisis Game

```
topSalesGames
topRatedGames
latestGames
mostReviewedGames
```

---

### Filter Data

```
gamesByGenre
reviewsByGame
purchasesByUser
```

Contoh request:

```
GET /games.php?action=gamesByGenre&id=2
GET /reviews.php?action=reviewsByGame&id=3
GET /purchases.php?action=purchasesByUser&id=1
```

---

# Halaman Dokumentasi API

File:

```
docs.php
```

Halaman ini harus menjadi **website dokumentasi API** yang berisi:

### 1. Base URL API

Contoh:

```
https://namadomain.com/api/
```

---

### 2. Daftar Endpoint

Tabel endpoint:

| Endpoint  | Method | Deskripsi           |
| --------- | ------ | ------------------- |
| users.php | GET    | mengambil data user |
| users.php | POST   | menambah user       |
| users.php | PUT    | update user         |
| users.php | DELETE | hapus user          |

---

### 3. Contoh Request

```
GET /games.php?action=topRatedGames
```

---

### 4. Contoh Response JSON

```
{
 "status": {
  "code": 200,
  "description": "Data berhasil diambil"
 },
 "result": []
}
```

